snippet.title: New Version Update: Anniversary Rave - Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
Welcome to the brand-new version of Honkai Impact 3rd: Anniversary Rave! The final battle will be fought in the Twilight of the Gods. Let the final conflagration begin.

Subscribe our YouTube and turn on notification for latest video : http://bit.ly/HonkaiImpact3rdYTB
